description: ABOUT US:  You may know Sweet E's Bake Shop from our popular store front on 3rd Street in West Hollywood, but did you know that we also have a dessert truck?  Imagine this: your favorite Sweet E’s treats, ON WHEELS!  You can find the Sweet E's dessert truck at food truck events all around the L.A. metro area and it is also available to rent for corporate affairs, birthday parties, weddings, or any other special event!WHAT WE SELL:  The Sweet E's truck carries a wide variety of mouth-watering sweets including cupcakes, cake pops, brownies, bars, cookies, and more!  We make a ton of flavors that will satisfy any sweet tooth.  We also may carry vegan or gluten free items for those with special diets, and our kitchen is certified Kosher.We look forward to baking for you!This great truck started in 2009, and quickly became a Los Angeles fixture. Why? Well, just take a look at their delicious sweets to find out: http://roaminghunger.com/blog/8078/a-sweet-tooth-for-sweet-es
name: Sweet E's Truck
